76c42e29-aee0-4613-a6d8-6497536d1da1.title: Paul
76c42e29-aee0-4613-a6d8-6497536d1da1.text:
Hello, <player>. I'm the Iron Man tutor.
What can I do for you?

options.text: I'd like to change my Iron Man mode.

aa97a24b-a5b2-46f7-aa42-250d1b8741e1.title: Paul
aa97a24b-a5b2-46f7-aa42-250d1b8741e1.text:
When you play as an Iron Man, you do everything
for yourself. You don't trade with other players, or take
their items, or accept their help.

0b2c9351-a430-4e0d-acac-0f725393eb05.title: Paul
0b2c9351-a430-4e0d-acac-0f725393eb05.text:
As an Iron Man, you choose to have these restrictions
imposed on you, so everyone knows you're doing it
properly.

48dca03a-89fe-4be1-9f08-7f5306414fc8.title: Paul
48dca03a-89fe-4be1-9f08-7f5306414fc8.text:
If you think you have what it takes, you can choose to
become a Hardcore Iron Man.

7580fbeb-66ef-407e-ae1d-1421737c864a.title: Paul
7580fbeb-66ef-407e-ae1d-1421737c864a.text:
In addition to the standard restrictions, Hardcore Iron
Man only have one life. In the event of a dangerous
death, your Hardcore Iron Man status will be
downgraded to that of a standard Iron Man, and your

7e21718c-2053-4ec0-8937-40f1b47a2b60.title: Paul
7e21718c-2053-4ec0-8937-40f1b47a2b60.text: stats will be frozen on the Hardcore Iron Man hiscores.

4f218a0f-95be-46d6-ba52-a892a8f92467.title: Paul
4f218a0f-95be-46d6-ba52-a892a8f92467.text:
For the ultimate challenge, you can choose to become
an Ultimate Iron Man, a game mode inspired by the
player IronNoBank.

a4004007-df75-439c-a460-22cbcb74da6f.title: Paul
a4004007-df75-439c-a460-22cbcb74da6f.text:
In addition to the standard restrictions, Ultimate Iron
Man are blocked from using the bank, and they drop all
their items when they die.

33d35b03-a520-4db1-b47c-b43d54d4641b.title: <player>
33d35b03-a520-4db1-b47c-b43d54d4641b.text: I'd like to change my Iron Man mode.

30537f8e-f6ba-4ef8-9565-1b6fcb8e5266.title: Paul
30537f8e-f6ba-4ef8-9565-1b6fcb8e5266.text:
While you're on Tutorial Island, you can switch freely
between being a standard Iron Man, an Ultimate Iron
Man, a Hardcore Iron Man or a normal player.

119a5ad3-9066-4fb6-8b35-40300ea18332.title: Paul
119a5ad3-9066-4fb6-8b35-40300ea18332.text:
Once you've left this island, you'll be able to find my
colleague Adam in Lumbridge, but he'll only let you
switch your restrictions downwards, not upwards.

816b3154-4773-4c8b-b4fe-fce4731a0363.title: Paul
816b3154-4773-4c8b-b4fe-fce4731a0363.text:
So he will let Hardcore Iron Man or Ultimate Iron
Man downgrade to standard Iron Man, and he'll let all
types of Iron Man become normal players.

08902e16-9c74-4a1c-8423-ae2c9f81f9de.title: Paul
08902e16-9c74-4a1c-8423-ae2c9f81f9de.text:
Make sure you've got your Iron Man settings all
sorted before you leave Tutorial Island. Some things
can't be changed later.
